T1  - How research agendas are framed: Insights for leadership, learning and spillover in science teams
AU  - O'Kane, Conor
AU  - Mangematin, Vincent
AU  - Zhang, Jing A.
AU  - Haar, Jarrod
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 53
IS  - 7
