T1  - “The reality in the DRC is just not the reality in Rwanda” – How context factors affect transdisciplinary research projects
AU  - Pärli, Rea
AU  - Byamungu, Moustapha
AU  - Fischer, Manuel
AU  - Kantengwa, Speciose
AU  - Kintche, Kokou
